description:
What if the entire Earth was transformed into a perfect and beautiful paradise? Imagine living in the presence of God Himself, where the tree of life bears eternal fruit, and a river of life flows abundantly. No more night, only the radiant glory of God! Join Elder Ted Wilson as he shares good news about a world where we reunite with our loved ones who were resurrected in the Lord. Watch the video and discover the amazing promises that await us! 

To watch the full video from Elder Ted Wilson, president of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, paste this link into your browser:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JhSKrUPurWE&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo_ANrUJhHN2_4bSlMDTjuqQ&index=65
